                                                            <div class="article-item">
                                                                The study investigated the levels of awareness, accessibility and impact of StarTimes and GOtv 
                                                                services on professional practices of academic library personnel in Edo State, Nigeria. Totted 
                                                                enumeration of library personnel in three university libraries - federal, state and 
                                                                private - was done using the survey method. Results revealed that while awareness was high, 
                                                                accessibility was average. Respondents accessed StarTimes and GOtv services at home through decoders 
                                                                and subscription. Over half the respondents watched StarTimes 
                                                                and GOtv. Respondents gave disparate purposes for watching Startimes and GOtv, however, they 
                                                                accessed the services mostly for current information and news. StarTimes and Gotv impacted  
                                                                respondents' professional practice as they learned general life's lessons that impacted 
                                                                their job performance positively, got current information to answer users' questions, watched 
                                                                programmes on job ethics, as well as other career-related programmes. Conclusively, the inclusion of more 
                                                                TV programmes tailored to the educational and professional needs of library personnel could enhance the impact 
                                                                of both StarTimes and GOtv in the State, and product sales for the companies.
